## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="a93ff-102">원본 이벤트에서 모든 이벤트 데이터 (추적 또는 디버그) 문자열로 ETW 하위 시스템에 기록 됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a93ff-102">All event data (trace or debug) from the source event is written to the ETW subsystem as a string.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a93ff-103">데이터 요소는 쉼표를 사용 하 여 구분 됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a93ff-103">The data elements are delimited using a comma.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a93ff-104">사용할 다른 구분 기호를 지정 하는 <xref:System.Diagnostics.Eventing.EventProviderTraceListener.Delimiter%2A> 속성입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a93ff-104">To specify a different delimiter, use the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Eventing.EventProviderTraceListener.Delimiter%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a93ff-105">수신기 추가 <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource?displayProperty=nameWithType> ETW 하위 시스템을 사용 하 여 공급자를 등록 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a93ff-105">Adding the listener to <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource?displayProperty=nameWithType> registers the provider with the ETW subsystem.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a93ff-106">이벤트 로그 파일에 쓸 Logman.exe 실행 프로그램 (또는 이와 유사한)를 사용 하 여 ETW 추적 세션을 만들어야 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a93ff-106">You must create an ETW trace session using the Logman.exe executable program (or something similar) to write the events to a log file.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a93ff-107">이벤트 데이터를 단일 문자열 이므로 수신기에서 이벤트를 사용 하는 매니페스트가 필요가 없습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a93ff-107">You do not need a manifest to consume events from the listener because the event data is a single string.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a93ff-108">호출 하는 경우는 <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource?displayProperty=nameWithType> 전달 이벤트를 기록 하는 메서드를 <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventType?displayProperty=nameWithType> 열거형 값입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a93ff-108">When you call the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource?displayProperty=nameWithType> methods to write events, you pass a <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventType?displayProperty=nameWithType> enumeration value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a93ff-109">수준과 키워드 값을 포함 하는 열거형입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a93ff-109">The enumeration contains both level and keyword values.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a93ff-110">사용자가 지정한 수준 값을 다음 중 하나를 사용 하 여 연결 된 값 수를 ETW 세션의 추적 수신기 공급자를 사용 하도록 설정 하면 <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventType?displayProperty=nameWithType> 열거형 값:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a93ff-110">When you enable a trace listener provider from an ETW session, the level value that you specify can be the value associated with one of the following <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventType?displayProperty=nameWithType> enumeration values:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="a93ff-111">중요 한 (값은 1)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a93ff-111">Critical (value is 1)</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="a93ff-112">오류 (값은 2 임)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a93ff-112">Error (value is 2)</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="a93ff-113">(값은 8) 정보</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a93ff-113">Information (value is 8)</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="a93ff-114">자세한 정보 (값은 16)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a93ff-114">Verbose (value is 16)</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="a93ff-115">경고 (값은 4)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a93ff-115">Warning (value is 4)</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a93ff-116">세션에는 다음 중 하나를 사용 하 여 연결 된 값 수에 지정 하는 키워드 값 <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventType?displayProperty=nameWithType> 열거형 값:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a93ff-116">The keyword value that you specify for the session can be the value associated with one of the following <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventType?displayProperty=nameWithType> enumeration values:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="a93ff-117">다시 시작 (가치가 2,048)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a93ff-117">Resume (value is 2,048)</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="a93ff-118">시작 (값은 256)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a93ff-118">Start (value is 256)</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="a93ff-119">중지 (값은 512)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a93ff-119">Stop (value is 512)</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="a93ff-120">일시 중단 (가치가 1,024)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a93ff-120">Suspend (value is 1,024)</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="a93ff-121">전송 (가치가 4,096)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a93ff-121">Transfer (value is 4,096)</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```csharp  
private static Guid providerId = new Guid("{B3F0C8FC-E8A8-4868-8901-1465E8A2F41B}");  
  
    EventProviderTraceListener listener = new EventProviderTraceListener(providerId.ToString(), "Test Listener", "::");  
  
    // You should use the All default level and control the level using the  
    // ETW session; otherwise, you may not log all the events requested by the  
    // session.  
    TraceSource source = new TraceSource("MyProvider", SourceLevels.All);  
  
    source.Listeners.Add(listener);  
  
    source.TraceData(TraceEventType.Warning | TraceEventType.Start, 2, new object[] { "abc", "def", true, 123 });  
  
    source.TraceEvent(TraceEventType.Warning, 12, "Provider guid: {0}", new object[] { providerId });  
  
    source.TraceInformation("string {0}, bool {1}, int {2}, ushort {3}", new object[] { "abc", false, 123, (UInt32)5 });  
```
